"----------------------------------------------------
" cursor moving in insert mode
"----------------------------------------------------
inoremap <C-j> <Down>
inoremap <C-k> <Up>
inoremap <C-b> <Left>
inoremap <C-f> <Right>
inoremap <C-l> <Right>
inoremap <C-d> <Right><ESC>xi
inoremap <C-o> <ESC>o

"----------------------------------------------------
" cursor moving in normal mode
"----------------------------------------------------
" search
nnoremap n nzz
nnoremap N Nzz
nnoremap * *zz
nnoremap # #zz
nnoremap g* g*zz
nnoremap g# g#zz
